WEBVTT

00:01.434 --> 00:03.001
Clarence:
Previously on "Clarence"...

00:03.003 --> 00:04.269
When the power went out,

00:04.271 --> 00:06.371
Mom and Chad pretended
that Jeff was me.

00:06.373 --> 00:08.740
But Jeff wasn't that good
at being me,

00:08.742 --> 00:10.776
so he mostly just cleaned up
a lot,

00:10.778 --> 00:12.744
which it freaked out my mom
and Chad

00:12.746 --> 00:14.846
'cause they thought
he was a robot.

00:14.848 --> 00:17.682
Everyone's wondering
where I went, and...

00:17.684 --> 00:18.750
Wait.

00:18.752 --> 00:20.285
Where am I?

00:20.287 --> 00:23.021
[ Laughing maniacally ]

00:23.023 --> 00:24.523
[ Remote clicks ]

00:24.525 --> 00:26.925
[ Upbeat music plays ]

00:29.530 --> 00:31.630
♪ I don't care what you say! ♪

00:32.632 --> 00:34.867
[ Soft acoustic guitar music
plays ]

00:34.869 --> 00:37.269
[ Thunder rumbles ]

00:43.043 --> 00:47.046
[ Gurgling, humming softly ]

00:48.381 --> 00:50.648
♪<i> We're Ums</i> ♪ - <i>I'm here
just North of Aberdale,</i>

00:50.650 --> 00:52.417
<i>and it's just awful!</i> ♪<i> We're
dum, we're Ums, um dum dum</i> ♪

00:52.419 --> 00:54.119
<i>I've never seen</i>
<i>anything like it!</i>

00:54.121 --> 00:56.554
♪<i> We live inside your bed</i> ♪
<i>It's a real gale!</i>

00:56.556 --> 00:58.056
♪<i> We live inside your socks</i> ♪ <i>I can
now report hail. There's hail here.</i>

00:58.058 --> 01:00.558
We're super, super fun,
we're Mmms!

01:00.560 --> 01:02.427
Oh, man,
that never gets old.

01:02.429 --> 01:05.229
[ Gasps ]
My slimy raisin drink!

01:05.231 --> 01:07.566
<i>Do not go outside</i>
<i>under any circumst--</i>

01:09.670 --> 01:11.670
[ Banjo music plays ]

01:11.672 --> 01:12.938
What?!

01:12.940 --> 01:14.406
Man!

01:14.408 --> 01:16.742
[ Grunting ]

01:18.645 --> 01:21.079
Oh, hello there.
[ Chuckles ]

01:21.081 --> 01:22.146
Beautiful day!

01:22.148 --> 01:25.584
Yup.
World's gonna end.

01:25.586 --> 01:27.285
That's too bad.

01:27.287 --> 01:30.155
[ Sumo grunting ]

01:30.157 --> 01:33.925
♪♪

01:33.927 --> 01:35.360
[ Hose creaks ]

01:37.497 --> 01:38.930
Knock, knock.

01:38.932 --> 01:40.365
[ Growls ]

01:40.367 --> 01:42.433
Ya drink it.

01:42.435 --> 01:44.836
Ya see?

01:44.838 --> 01:46.672
There ya go!

01:47.675 --> 01:51.008
What?
[ Groans ]

01:51.010 --> 01:53.679
[ Sighs ]

01:58.118 --> 01:59.551
Hmm.

01:59.553 --> 02:01.619
[ Wind whistling ]

02:01.621 --> 02:04.389
Tinona,
- can you get the kids, please?

02:05.158 --> 02:06.224
Is this a drill?

02:06.226 --> 02:07.492
Mnh-mnh.

02:07.494 --> 02:08.826
There ain't no way to say this,

02:08.828 --> 02:10.495
but the planet's getting warmer,

02:10.497 --> 02:13.298
bees are dying, dollar won't buy
what it used to.

02:13.300 --> 02:14.298
What?!

02:14.300 --> 02:16.701
[ Yawns ]

02:16.703 --> 02:18.236
Aww!    Aww!
Aww!            Aww!

02:18.238 --> 02:19.637
Family,
we don't got time

02:19.639 --> 02:21.306
to gush
over some critter!

02:21.308 --> 02:22.307
Careful, Dad!

02:22.309 --> 02:23.308
Ow!

02:23.310 --> 02:24.475
She bites.

02:24.477 --> 02:25.744
This critter's
gonna get buried

02:25.746 --> 02:27.145
six feet under water,

02:27.147 --> 02:29.848
and so will we
- if we don't prepare properly.

02:29.850 --> 02:31.316
[ Growling ]

02:31.318 --> 02:32.483
Sumo, put her outside.

02:32.485 --> 02:34.319
But, Dad,
I think she's an orphan!

02:34.321 --> 02:38.389
If it's not family,
it's just another mouth to feed.

02:38.391 --> 02:39.858
[ Giggling ]

02:39.860 --> 02:40.658
What?

02:40.660 --> 02:41.660
Huh?
- Hmm?

02:41.662 --> 02:42.861
[ Thunder rumbles ]

02:42.863 --> 02:44.529
Now, this blue line
is forest fires,

02:44.531 --> 02:46.231
and the orange right here,
that's typhus.

02:46.233 --> 02:48.900
Now, you're gonna have to figure
out what you're gonna do.

02:48.902 --> 02:51.003
Now, let's try
a little thought experiment.

02:51.005 --> 02:53.371
Pretend this basketball
is the Earth,

02:53.373 --> 02:55.841
and my fist is gamma rays.

02:55.843 --> 02:56.742
Pow!

02:56.744 --> 02:58.343
Only the moon men survive.

02:58.345 --> 03:00.178
Shh.
Ow!

03:00.180 --> 03:03.182
Now, you might think it's silly
to practice in the rain,

03:03.184 --> 03:06.918
but this is simulating
real life conditions here.

03:06.920 --> 03:09.521
In a high-wind type
situation,

03:09.523 --> 03:11.790
you're gonna want
to tie yourself up to a buddy

03:11.792 --> 03:13.091
using a six-foot rope.

03:13.093 --> 03:14.025
Whoa!

03:14.027 --> 03:15.526
Family,
this is important,

03:15.528 --> 03:17.028
so I'm only gonna
do this once.

03:17.030 --> 03:20.064
Hey, dad, can I go to Clarence's
for a sleepover?

03:20.066 --> 03:21.199
Negative.

03:21.201 --> 03:24.135
Tonight, we're doing
radioactive preparation.

03:24.137 --> 03:25.203
Sorry.

03:25.205 --> 03:26.370
My dad's making us do

03:26.372 --> 03:27.639
these stupid
doomsday drills.

03:27.641 --> 03:28.906
[ Chomp! ]
- Ow!

03:28.908 --> 03:30.542
Quit blabbing
about slumber parties!

03:30.544 --> 03:31.743
I'm coming!

03:31.745 --> 03:32.877
Clarence: Wait,
so now you are coming?

03:32.879 --> 03:34.212
No,
- I was talking to my dad.

03:34.214 --> 03:36.915
Sumo, this could save your --
[ Grunts ]

03:36.917 --> 03:39.384
[ Laughs ]

03:39.386 --> 03:41.152
[ Eerie music plays ]

03:41.154 --> 03:45.390
Uh, Dad, are we over-watering
these plants?

03:45.392 --> 03:46.792
[ Air horn honks ]

03:46.794 --> 03:49.160
I want to see those knees
up in the air.

03:49.162 --> 03:51.162
Go, go, go!
Jump!

03:51.164 --> 03:53.398
Can we go inside already?!

03:53.400 --> 03:56.901
Now, Sumo, you got three seconds
to get your mask back on

03:56.903 --> 03:59.303
before you're completely
contaminated.

03:59.305 --> 04:01.640
Three, two, one...

04:01.642 --> 04:03.608
and you're toast.

04:03.610 --> 04:05.010
You're crazy!

04:05.012 --> 04:07.078
Remember how you said
the chickens wouldn't lay eggs

04:07.080 --> 04:08.180
because of the eclipse?

04:08.182 --> 04:09.247
Sumo, this could --

04:09.249 --> 04:10.248
[ Electricity crackles ]

04:10.250 --> 04:12.650
What?

04:12.652 --> 04:14.919
Protocol 22!

04:14.921 --> 04:18.656
Protocol 22!
Protocol 22!

04:18.658 --> 04:20.591
Dad, it's just...

04:20.593 --> 04:23.528
[ Dramatic rock music plays ]

04:23.530 --> 04:25.697
[ Engine starts ]

04:32.305 --> 04:34.939
[ All murmuring ]

04:34.941 --> 04:38.443
Tanner: [ Chuckles ] Everybody
in school is gonna love me now.

04:38.445 --> 04:42.013
Family, welcome to your new
home.

04:42.015 --> 04:45.516
-Ooh! -Yeah! -Wow!

04:45.518 --> 04:47.285
[ Animal chittering ]
Ooh! Aah!

04:47.287 --> 04:48.286
[ Grunts ]

04:48.288 --> 04:49.955
[ Chomp! ]
Ow!

04:51.291 --> 04:56.227
Uh, I-I mean, wow!

04:56.229 --> 04:58.129
Told you they'd love it.

04:58.131 --> 04:59.964
Well, come on.
Let me show y'all around.

04:59.966 --> 05:01.199
You got your dining area...

05:01.201 --> 05:02.901
-Yeah! -Whoa! -Look at that!

05:02.903 --> 05:05.069
And in here, enough beans
to make a farmer blush.

05:05.071 --> 05:08.806
You got your sleeping area
with radio for sweet lullabies.

05:08.808 --> 05:10.408
Ms. Baker:<i> Hello?</i>
<i>Is anyone out there?!</i>

05:10.410 --> 05:11.676
<i>We need help! Help!</i>
[ Radio clicks off ]

05:11.678 --> 05:12.677
That's enough of that.

05:12.679 --> 05:14.012
Over here's the aquarium,

05:14.014 --> 05:15.814
so Lil' Brandi
can be a mermaid.

05:15.816 --> 05:18.249
Oh!
How'd you know?!

05:18.251 --> 05:20.484
Over there's the entertainment
console.

05:20.486 --> 05:22.053
Get out of here.
I'm first!

05:22.055 --> 05:25.323
This is the bucket corner
for all your bucket needs...

05:25.325 --> 05:27.058
now with a privacy curtain.

05:27.060 --> 05:29.493
And right next door
is the fun hump...

05:29.495 --> 05:30.895
Should keep Sumo
entertained.

05:30.897 --> 05:32.764
[ Scoffs ]
Yeah, sure will.

05:32.766 --> 05:34.332
This is where
you'll have school

05:34.334 --> 05:37.168
because, in a ruthless world,
only the cunning survive.

05:37.170 --> 05:39.671
Right above your heads,
here's your new sun,

05:39.673 --> 05:41.039
diesel-powered.

05:41.041 --> 05:42.908
Over here, we've got
your zombie apocalypse kit,

05:42.910 --> 05:44.009
your lizard-man repellent.

05:44.011 --> 05:45.376
[ Grunts ]
Quit biting!

05:45.378 --> 05:47.845
[ Animal chittering ]
Your vampire kit...

05:47.847 --> 05:49.847
[ Laughter and cheering ]

05:49.849 --> 05:51.049
Huh?
[ Chomp! ]

05:51.051 --> 05:51.850
Ow!

05:51.852 --> 05:53.218
Dad, she didn't mean it!

05:53.220 --> 05:54.853
This isn't a discussion.

05:54.855 --> 05:56.721
Critters aren't part
of this family.

05:56.723 --> 05:58.189
What!?
What about the dogs?!

05:58.191 --> 06:00.625
The house
belongs to them now.

06:00.627 --> 06:03.562
[ Dogs howling, barking ]

06:05.432 --> 06:09.134
So we're just gonna live here
forever like mole people?

06:09.136 --> 06:11.536
I bet the power will be back on
any second.

06:11.538 --> 06:13.138
All right,
lets take a vote.

06:13.140 --> 06:15.073
Who wants to stay
in the shelter?

06:15.075 --> 06:16.407
Yeah!

06:16.409 --> 06:18.309
I like being a mermaid.

06:18.311 --> 06:20.412
And who wants to live outside
with the critters?

06:20.414 --> 06:22.714
[ Growling ]

06:22.716 --> 06:25.150
[ Scoffs, mutters ]

06:27.821 --> 06:31.222
[ Whimpers ]

06:31.224 --> 06:32.323
Go on! Git!

06:32.325 --> 06:34.659
[ Whines ]

06:35.629 --> 06:37.461
[ Yells ]
Go on! Git!

06:37.463 --> 06:39.563
Aah!

06:39.565 --> 06:43.168
Ah!
That bucket works great.

06:44.971 --> 06:47.405
Nothing goes in or out,
understand?

06:47.407 --> 06:49.341
Yeah, sure.

06:49.343 --> 06:51.076
All right.
Who's hungry?

06:52.012 --> 06:53.144
♪♪

06:53.146 --> 06:55.614
Now aren't we just blessed
from above

06:55.616 --> 06:58.183
to have such a bounty
in the end times?

06:58.185 --> 06:59.918
Yuck!

07:03.290 --> 07:05.089
I want that!

07:05.091 --> 07:07.358
We'll have that
at Christmas, Sumo.

07:07.360 --> 07:09.094
Eat your liver.

07:13.200 --> 07:15.367
Sumo, could you pass
the ketchup?

07:16.670 --> 07:18.837
Nah!
Sumo can do it.

07:20.974 --> 07:24.442
Sumo, I am pretty sure you knew
that's not what I meant.

07:24.444 --> 07:26.010
Seems like Sumo
doesn't care

07:26.012 --> 07:29.113
about having ketchup
in the apocalypse.

07:29.115 --> 07:31.216
Hope everybody here
likes dry meat.

07:31.218 --> 07:32.984
[ Chair scraping ]
Ah, okay.

07:32.986 --> 07:35.353
All right yeah.
Yeah, Sumo, very nice.

07:35.355 --> 07:36.521
There he goes.

07:36.523 --> 07:38.956
Yep, you have fun over there
on your fun hump.

07:38.958 --> 07:41.459
Tanner, can you pass
some mustard?

07:41.461 --> 07:43.228
[ Chimes jingling ]

07:48.135 --> 07:49.166
[ Sighs ]

07:49.168 --> 07:51.502
I don't know what to do
about Sumo.

07:51.504 --> 07:53.138
That boy
just doesn't listen.

07:53.140 --> 07:56.041
Wonder where
he gets that from.

07:56.043 --> 07:57.409
What?

07:59.146 --> 08:01.479
[ Rain falling ]

08:01.481 --> 08:02.480
Oh.

08:02.482 --> 08:03.848
What y'all looking at?

08:03.850 --> 08:06.551
♪♪

08:06.553 --> 08:07.985
Sumo, I...

08:07.987 --> 08:09.654
Look, you can't...

08:09.656 --> 08:11.989
You know what I mean.

08:11.991 --> 08:15.160
Sumo, come on.
- Just take the dang pudding.

08:16.329 --> 08:17.328
Sumo?

08:17.330 --> 08:18.830
♪♪

08:18.832 --> 08:20.165
What?

08:21.668 --> 08:22.900
[ Dramatic music plays ]

08:22.902 --> 08:24.936
[ Thunder cracks ]

08:24.938 --> 08:26.437
[ Wind howling ]

08:26.439 --> 08:29.207
[ Grunting ]

08:30.610 --> 08:32.243
[ Shivering ]

08:32.245 --> 08:35.914
Sumo!
Sumo, where are ya, boy?!

08:37.117 --> 08:39.350
Sumo: Come on, girl, we gotta get out.
- [ Growls ]

08:39.352 --> 08:40.185
Ow!

08:40.187 --> 08:41.786
Sumo, what are you doing?!

08:41.788 --> 08:43.287
Go away!
It's dangerous.

08:43.289 --> 08:44.355
I'm tying you off!

08:44.357 --> 08:45.289
Stop!

08:45.291 --> 08:46.924
I'm not leaving
without Candice!

08:46.926 --> 08:48.560
Sumo, we don't got time
to be naming critters

08:48.562 --> 08:49.727
and hiding in dog houses!

08:49.729 --> 08:51.463
Let go! Ow!
- Stop.

08:51.465 --> 08:52.697
We gotta get out of here!

08:52.699 --> 08:54.032
No!
- Sumo, come on!

08:54.034 --> 08:55.800
No!
- Come on!

08:55.802 --> 08:57.368
Aah! Gah!

08:57.370 --> 08:59.104
Dad!

09:05.045 --> 09:06.611
Aaaaaah!
[ Chomp! ]

09:06.613 --> 09:07.712
Huh?

09:07.714 --> 09:10.248
[ Growling ]

09:10.250 --> 09:13.384
Aaaaaah!

09:13.386 --> 09:17.254
[ Old timey music playing
on radio ]

09:17.256 --> 09:18.589
Ohh!

09:18.591 --> 09:20.424
[ Groans ]
Sumo!

09:20.426 --> 09:21.759
Candice?

09:21.761 --> 09:23.495
You okay?

09:23.497 --> 09:24.729
Come on, girl!

09:24.731 --> 09:26.898
Stay with me, Candice,
stay with me!

09:26.900 --> 09:30.501
[ Sad music plays ]

09:30.503 --> 09:32.404
I'm sorry, Sumo.

09:35.275 --> 09:36.274
[ Chomp! ]

09:36.276 --> 09:37.409
Ow!

09:39.079 --> 09:41.246
Ah, dang! Really?! - Come back!

09:42.416 --> 09:44.082
[ Candice squeals ]

09:44.084 --> 09:45.116
Oh, no!
Candice!

09:45.118 --> 09:46.951
Sumo, wait!
No, Candice!

09:46.953 --> 09:49.153
Dad, she saved us!
We gotta save her!

09:49.155 --> 09:52.924
Aaaaaaah!

09:58.765 --> 09:59.964
[ Objects clattering ]

09:59.966 --> 10:02.333
Dad,
what are you doing?

10:02.335 --> 10:04.602
Sumo, that critter
saved us back there.

10:04.604 --> 10:05.637
She's family now,

10:05.639 --> 10:07.171
and we don't
leave family behind.

10:07.173 --> 10:08.439
We're gonna go get her?

10:08.441 --> 10:10.975
Yup, and we ain't
coming back till--

10:10.977 --> 10:12.610
♪♪

10:12.612 --> 10:14.779
Uh, Dad, uh...

10:14.781 --> 10:18.049
I lo-- I lo-- I lov--

10:18.051 --> 10:20.451
Yeah,
I know what you mean.

10:20.453 --> 10:24.322
I, earlier, I was,
um pudding, uh...

10:24.324 --> 10:26.123
I know what you mean,
Dad.

10:26.125 --> 10:29.460
Tinona,
can I borrow your truck?

10:29.462 --> 10:30.562
What for?

10:30.564 --> 10:32.963
Sumo's got a friend
out in the storm.

10:32.965 --> 10:34.298
We're gonna go get her.

10:34.300 --> 10:36.467
[ Sighs ]

10:36.469 --> 10:38.002
Okay.

10:38.004 --> 10:39.003
Thanks, hon, I--

10:39.005 --> 10:40.972
Don't scratch it.

10:40.974 --> 10:42.373
[ Chuckles ]

10:42.375 --> 10:43.407
Course not.

10:43.409 --> 10:44.976
Thanks, babe.

10:44.978 --> 10:46.644
Sumo, you ready?

10:46.646 --> 10:47.678
Yeah!

10:47.680 --> 10:49.980
Dad, what are you do--

10:49.982 --> 10:52.317
I thought I told y'all
to go back to sleep.

10:52.319 --> 10:54.419
Whoa!

10:54.421 --> 10:56.253
[ Laughs ]

10:56.255 --> 10:58.889
Awesome!

10:58.891 --> 11:01.926
Yeah!
[ Laughs ]

11:03.729 --> 11:05.563
♪ Early to bed ♪

11:07.100 --> 11:09.200
♪ Early to rise ♪

11:10.737 --> 11:13.605
♪ Picking my nose ♪
